<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="18Feb1921"><font color="red">18 February 1921</font>, <cite>Letters III</cite> (JJ to Carlo Linati): I&apos;m working like a convict until 3 or 4 in the morning. I finished <cite>Circe</cite> and <cite>Eumeus</cite>. The last two episodes that are left, <cite>Ithaca</cite> and <cite>Penelope</cite> are also giving me a hard time</div>
